  lines:
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 04c44a04ade27492284b5d1eb85ad4fe, type: 2}
    text: "Oh, hey. Have you seen Ritsu? He\u2019s been dodging my texts all morning.
      It\u2019s starting to get suspicious."
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c0b6716d4b3ae41488323461179cf4a7, type: 2}
    text: Ritsu? Uh, last I saw him, he looked... very busy. With school stuff. Definitely
      not avoiding you.
